				Training Package, the Face to Face Training Package also includes one on one 
				time with the trainer during your weekly meeting, and your weekly 
				communication session online.<strong><%= link_to "  Click here ",    training_programs_path %></strong>
			      	for more information regarding the Face to Face Training Package.</p>
